resources.string: Ukuba uyonwabela le app ndiyivelisile, nceda ucinge ngokuthenga iapp yam.
Uhlelo lokusebenza lomnikelo alwenzi kwanto, kodwa umnikelo wakho uyakundibonisa ukuba ixesha lam elichithwe kuphuculo lwasimahla, akukho zintengiso ziyaxatyiswa.
Ukuba uyonwabela le app ndiyivelisile, nceda ucinge ngokuthenga usetyenziso lwam.

Uhlelo lokusebenza lokuphucula lubandakanya iibhokisi zokutshekisha ukumakisha xa uphelelwe yimali okanye imali, kwaye ukuthengwa kwakho kuya kundibonisa ukuba ixesha lam elichithwe kuphuculo lwasimahla, akukho nazintengiso ziyaxatyiswa.
